title: Tua and Tyreek in Miami, Sean McVay Wedding, QB's in The Match, and Surprise playoff teams
itunes:title: Tua and Tyreek in Miami, Sean McVay Wedding, QB's in The Match, and Surprise playoff teams
description:
The Good Morning Football Podcast returns with Tua Tagovailoa and Tyreek Hill giving the Dolphins a fresh start.  Hosts Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt, Will Selva, and Fmr NFL RB Maurice Jones-Drew discuss other storylines this offseason that are overrated.  Peter takes us inside Sean McVay's wedding this past weekend before expressing concerns with Aaron Rodgers mentality in 'The Match'.  The table also gives their surprise playoff teams this year with Kyle picking the Vikings and MJD explaining how the Colts can shock the world.

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
